snippet.title: Behind the scenes look at Amber Heard's Company cover shoot
snippet.description:
Subscribe to TheShowbiz411! http://bit.ly/tsb411yt
Check out Amber Heard behind the scenes on her Company magazine cover shoot. Johnny Depp's beautiful actor girlfriend takes centre stage for December's addition and also does an interview.

On the subject of relationships and love she says: "It is really hard when you spend your life living out of a suitcase. But it really does weed out superficial people -- if someone is still with you after the second movie then they're probably a good one! I like to trust people in general -- it's the southern girl in me." Report by James Sloan.
